<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="institutions-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Our Institutions</h1>
                <p>Nageshwaram Foundation Trust is dedicated to fostering educational excellence through its growing network of institutions.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="current-institutions-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>N.R.K. Public School</h2>
                <div class="institution-card">
                    <img src="/public/images/school-placeholder.svg" alt="N.R.K. Public School" class="institution-image">
                    <div class="institution-details">
                        <h3>A Pillar of Quality School Education</h3>
                        <p>N.R.K. Public School, nestled in Shastri Nagar, Batiya, Jamui, Bihar, stands as a testament to our commitment to foundational education. Since its inception, the school has been a beacon of learning, providing a nurturing environment for students from pre-nursery to higher secondary levels. We focus on a comprehensive curriculum that not only excels in academics but also emphasizes character development, sports, and extracurricular activities.</p>
                        <p>Our dedicated faculty, modern facilities, and student-centric approach ensure that every child receives personalized attention and the opportunity to unlock their full potential. We pride ourselves on fostering an inclusive learning community that prepares students for success in both higher education and life.</p>
                        <a href="/school" class="cta-button primary">Visit N.R.K. Public School Website</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="future-plans-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Expanding Our Educational Horizon</h2>
                <h3>Future College Integration</h3>
                <p>Building on the success and strong foundation laid by N.R.K. Public School, Nageshwaram Foundation Trust is ambitiously planning to establish a state-of-the-art college. This new institution will aim to provide advanced education and vocational training programs, catering to the growing aspirations of our youth in rural areas.</p>
                <p>The college will focus on offering courses that are relevant to emerging industries, equipped with modern laboratories, experienced faculty, and industry partnerships to ensure our students are job-ready and capable of contributing to the national economy. This initiative is a crucial step in fulfilling our vision of providing a complete educational ecosystem from early childhood to higher learning.</p>
                <p>Stay tuned for more updates on this exciting new chapter!</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="cta-button secondary">Learn More About Future Plans</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
